    public class HomologyBasisTracker<U extends PrimitiveBasisElement>
extends java.lang.Object
implements AbstractHomologyTracker<java.lang.Integer,java.lang.Integer,U,edu.stanford.math.primitivelib.autogen.formal_sum.IntSparseFormalSum<U>>
    This class maintains the right-filtration for performing zig-zag homology. It implements the algorithm described in the paper "Zigzag Persistent Homology and Real-valued Functions" by Gunnar Carlsson, Vin de Silva, and Dmitriy Morozov. TODO List: - cache low values for the columns to prevent re-computing
    Author:
    Andrew Tausz
